message.body: Hi Mom! Happy weekend! How is everything going?

Sitting in Little India on Moody st Waltham about to enjoy some lamb biryani with your handsome daddy...as a Free Woman. 1/2 hr ago I delivered & received my last hug on NB1. Lots to tell u & extreeemely eager to hear about your...well, everything! When this wkend would u like to talk?
